<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Faktura {{ invoiceNumber }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #570df8;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .invoice-details {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .invoice-details table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .invoice-details td {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .invoice-details td:first-child {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
            width: 40%;
        }
        .invoice-details tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .amount-highlight {
            background-color: #f0f0ff;
            border: 1px solid #570df8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .amount-highlight strong {
            color: #570df8;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Faktura {{ invoiceNumber }}</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>{{ name }},</h2>

        <p>v priloze najdete fakturu za pronajem skladoveho boxu.</p>

        <div class="amount-highlight">
            <strong>Castka: {{ amount }}</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="invoice-details">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Cislo faktury:</td>
                    <td><strong>{{ invoiceNumber }}</strong></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Datum vystaveni:</td>
                    <td>{{ issuedAt }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Misto:</td>
                    <td>{{ placeName }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Typ skladu:</td>
                    <td>{{ storageType }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Cislo boxu:</td>
                    <td>{{ storageNumber }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <p>Faktura je prilozena k tomuto emailu ve formatu PDF.</p>

        <p>Dekujeme za duveru!</p>

        <p>S pozdravem,<br>
        <strong>Tym Fajne Sklady</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Toto je automaticky generovany email. Prosim neodpovidejte na tuto zpravu.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} Fajne Sklady. Vsechna prava vyhrazena.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
